wiki.summary: “Sleeping on the Floor” has Future and Lil Uzi talking about their drug use, money, and women. Future flexes his lavish lifestyle rapping about his name brand clothes and diamonds, far enough to say he wears “more Gucci than Gucci.” Uzi uses his signature fast paced rap style to rap about how much money he has and how no one wants to beef with him. He continues to rap about how because he has money, women just flock to him in two’s. Read more on Last.fm.
